OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FEvery week - stop and think about this
OL,7,F- every single week, two women in
OL,8,FEngland and Wales are killed in these
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,FIt's a statistic which shames Britain
OL,12,F- and which has become so shockingly
OL,13,Froutine, it rarely makes the news.
OL,15,FAnd here is another fact which may
OL,16,Fshock you - which you might not be
OL,17,Faware of.
OL,19,FIf a woman is stabbed to death in the
OL,20,Fstreet by a stranger, the starting
OL,21,Fpoint for sentencing is 25 years.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/16
