OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FIf the same woman is stabbed to death
OL,7,Fwith a kitchen knife in her own home -
OL,8,Fthe starting point for sentencing is
OL,9,F15 years.
OL,11,FIt's a disparity which has prompted a
OL,12,Fgrowing campaign for change, and on
OL,13,Fwhich the government has been running
OL,14,Fa public consultation which closes on
OL,15,FMarch 4.
OL,17,FAs the clock ticks down to that date -
OL,18,Fnow just days away - I've been
OL,19,Finvestigating the issue for the
OL,20,FTonight programme.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/16
