OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FIt's more complex than you might think.
OL,8,FBut the stories of the families who've
OL,9,Flost beloved daughters to domestic
OL,10,Fhomicide are some of the most
OL,11,Fharrowing I have ever heard. We've
OL,12,Falso spoken to a brave woman who
OL,13,Fsurvived the most appalling knife
OL,14,Fattack by her partner, and we have had
OL,15,Frare access to a refuge - which
OL,16,Fprovides emergency shelter for those
OL,17,Fin mortal danger in their own homes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/16
