OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FUntil they heard the sentences given
OL,7,Fto the men.
OL,9,FPoppy's killer got 16 years. She had
OL,10,Fbeen stabbed repeatedly in her head
OL,11,Fand body, in her bed. A hundred
OL,12,Finjuries. She couldn't cry out for
OL,13,Fhelp because he cut her throat.
OL,15,FEllie's killer got 12 and a half
OL,16,Fyears, because he too was 17. He had
OL,17,Fleft the knife in her neck to try to
OL,18,Fclaim she'd killed herself.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/16
