OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FMegan's killer got 23 years: his
OL,7,Fsentence extended by the judge because
OL,8,Fof so many disturbing aggravating
OL,9,Ffactors. He had almost decapitated
OL,10,Fher, and drove her body away from the
OL,11,Fhouse to dump it.
OL,13,FIf the sentencing rules were changed,
OL,14,Fthe minimum would be 25 years for
OL,15,Fadults.
OL,17,FSo why is there such a disparity in
OL,18,Fsentencing?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/16
