OL,3,CMothers whose daughters were killed by
OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FAs I said - there are complexities in
OL,7,Fthis issue.
OL,9,FWhat about the cases - admittedly very
OL,10,Fsmall in number - where a woman who
OL,11,Fhas suffered long term abuse by her
OL,12,Fpartner, grabs a knife from the
OL,13,Fkitchen drawer and kills him?
OL,15,FShe would then potentially be subject
OL,16,Fto a minimum tariff of the 25 years
OL,17,Ftoo. Clare Wade and others - not least
OL,18,FHarriet Wistrich, founder of the
OL,19,FCentre for Women's Justice - say this
OL,20,Fuprate in the minimum sentencing could
OL,21,Fin fact be detrimental to some women.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
