OL,4,Cpartners campaign for harsher sentences
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with the
OL,8,Ffamilies of all those murdered in
OL,9,Fhorrendous circumstances by partners
OL,10,For ex-partners.
OL,12,F"The government has taken decisive
OL,13,Faction to ensure domestic killers are
OL,14,Flocked up for longer. We're making
OL,15,Fkilling at the end of a relationship,
OL,16,Fusing excessive violence and coercive
OL,17,For controlling behaviour statutory
OL,18,Faggravating factors for murder, and
OL,19,Ffor manslaughter involving sexual
OL,20,Fconduct.
